# Build context for `gcloud builds submit` (exploration 0205).
#
# Cloud Build uploads the repo as the build context. The control-plane and hub
# Dockerfiles only need the pnpm workspace manifests + packages/ + the app dir,
# so keep the upload small and fast. (BuildKit reads apps/cloud/Dockerfile.dockerignore
# for local `docker build`; Cloud Build reads THIS file instead.)
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.astro
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
.claude
docs
site
# Never upload local secrets / env files.
.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*
